+Start
+/ KNOWN BEHAVIOR: cache key uses literal step text (%var% not resolved)
+/ so the same step with different variable values returns cached result
+- save 'dynkey1.txt' with content 'content1'
+- save 'dynkey2.txt' with content 'content2'
+- set %fileName% = "dynkey1.txt"
+- call ReadDynamic
+- set %result1% = %dynContent%
